Type: Package
Package: lbstproj
Title: Tools To Create And Use Standardized R Projects For The L-Biostat
    Group
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexandre", "Bohyn", , "alexandre.bohyn@kuleuven.be", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9776-7467"))
Description: This package provides functions to easily start a new
    statistical analysis project in R. It creates a standardized folder
    structure and files, to allow for easier collaboration and
    reproducible research.  It also provides functions to easily load and
    preprocess data, generate and export figures and tables, and create
    reports in various formats.
